com.evite.qv.model
Class QVEvent

java.lang.Object
  com.evite.qv.model.QVEvent
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.io.Serializable
public class QVEvent
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable

QVEvent represents a simplified version of the EventsObject for use with the QVWebService. This hides our internal object so that we may refactor internally without having to change the webservice interface.

Version:
